  {
    "id": "minimax",
    "name": "MiniMax",
    "baseUrl": "https://api.minimaxi.com/v1",
    "docsUrl": "https://platform.minimaxi.com/docs/api-reference/text/chat-completion",
    "authScheme": "bearer",
    "apiFormat": "openai_chat",
    "models": {
      "default": "MiniMax-M2.7"
    },
    "modelCapabilities": {},
    "notices": [
      {
        "type": "info",
        "text": "MiniMax M2.x 走 OpenAI 兼容 chat completions 端点,代理自动剥不兼容字段(reasoning_effort / response_format / parallel_tool_calls 等)+ tool 剥 strict + 连续 system 合并;响应侧 reasoning_details 拆 reasoning + <think> 兜底拆分仅对 MiniMax 启用。"
      },
      {
        "type": "info",
        "text": "MiniMax chat completions API 当前不支持原生 web_search 工具(文档实证 2026-05-09)。如需联网搜索,推荐配 mcp_servers 使用 MCP 路径(参考 P5 namespace MCP 修复)。"
      }
    ],
    "requestOptions": {},
    "isBuiltin": true
  },
  {
    "id": "google-ai-studio",
    "name": "Google AI Studio",
    "baseUrl": "https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com",
    "docsUrl": "https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs",
    "authScheme": "google_api_key",
    "apiFormat": "gemini_native",
    "models": {
      "default": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite"
    },
    "modelCapabilities": {},
    "notices": [
      {
        "type": "info",
        "text": "Google AI Studio Gemini API 走 native `generateContent` / `streamGenerateContent` endpoint(`/v1alpha` for Gemini 3+, `/v1beta` for 2.x)。鉴权用 GEMINI_API_KEY(走 `x-goog-api-key` header,不是 Bearer)。代理把 Codex.app 的 Responses API 入站直接转 Gemini 原生 wire,响应侧 Gemini SSE 直转 OpenAI Responses SSE,不走 OpenAI compat 中间层。"
      },
      {
        "type": "info",
        "text": "Gemini 3.x 默认 dynamic thinking 已开启(Pro/Flash 默认 high)。代理把 Codex.app `reasoning.effort` 映射成 Gemini 3 用 `thinkingLevel`(low/medium/high),Gemini 2.x 用 `thinkingBudget`(1024/8192/16384)。Gemini 3.x 默认 `temperature=1.0`(LiteLLM 实证 < 1 触发 infinite loop)。"
      },
      {
        "type": "info",
        "text": "**Google Search grounding 已 work**:打开 web_search 工具后(Codex.app 默认开),代理把入站 OpenAI 标准 `web_search` 工具转 Gemini `tools=[{googleSearch:{}}]`。响应侧 grounding citations(`groundingMetadata.groundingChunks/groundingSupports`)直接 emit 成 Responses `response.output_text.annotation.added` 事件,Codex.app UI 显示来源链接。"
      },
      {
        "type": "warning",
        "text": "已知限制:① 3.x 文本模型当前**仍为 Preview**(`-preview` 后缀);未来 GA 后模型 ID 可能去掉 `-preview`,届时需手动改 mapping。② `generativelanguage.googleapis.com` 在中国大陆未直连,需 VPN。③ `gemini-3.1-flash-lite` 是当前唯一不带 `-preview` 的 stable 3.x,但能力为轻量级。④ Gemini 免费 tier 对 3.x Pro `limit:0`(实测 2026-05-10 触发 429 RESOURCE_EXHAUSTED),需在 Google AI Studio console 启用 billing 才能跑 gemini-3.1-pro-preview。"
      }
    ],
    "requestOptions": {},
    "isBuiltin": true
  }
]
